        <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#4F46E5]">Series A 투자 유치 완료</span>
        <i class="fas fa-arrow-right text-[#4F46E5] text-xs"></i>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold leading-tight mt-8 mobile-title reveal" style="--delay: 1;">
        비즈니스의 성장을<br>
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-[#4F46E5] to-[#7C3AED]">가속화하세요</span>
